descriptionHTML:
Have you ever envied the secrets agents and militants with super gadgets and watches? If you have then don’t envy anymore, if you own a smartwatch and want a cool pack of amazing themes for your wear its right here. Military watch bundle is designed keeping in mind rangers and militant type watches. With this collection you can enjoy three different styles of watch faces each with dozens of custom features. Awesome built-in features include ambient mode of all the styles, weather information, Battery status, Missed call Notifications, date, time and much more.

Frillroid Watch Faces focus is in creating professional looking watch faces. Each Watch Face is engineered by high quality design and required keen concentration to choose the watch colors with soothing effect which ultimately makes the watch unmatchable and incomparable.

Key custom features:-
• Latest Weather updates
• Classic Design
• Ultimate readability
• Clean and simplistic look
• Hi contrast and high colors
• Remaining battery life of your device so you exactly know when to charge
• Ambient mode engineered with the latest wear Api makes your watch’s battery stronger than ever

This watch face collection is for round/circular smart watches such as the Motorola Moto 360, LG G WATCH R and LG watch Urbane. Visit our exclusive Watch face collection for Android Wear on our website www.frillroid.com.

How it works?
It’s simple just download the app to your smartphone and sync it with the watch. The watch face that you will choose will be displayed on your watch screen. Open Settings from Android Wear app to customize the Watch Face. Get this app now and provide us your feedback :)
